---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about ToolMixr - free online tools for developers, designers, and content creators.">
  
  <div class="about-page">
    <h1>About ToolMixr</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Free online tools that respect your privacy.</p>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>What is ToolMixr?</h2>
      <p>ToolMixr is a collection of free online tools built for developers, designers, SEO specialists, and content creators. Every tool runs <strong>entirely in your browser</strong> — no data is ever sent to a server, no sign-up required, no tracking.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Why ToolMixr?</h2>
      <p>We got tired of online tools that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Force you to create an account just to format some JSON</li>
        <li>Upload your data to unknown servers for "processing"</li>
        <li>Bombard you with pop-ups, ads, and paywalls</li>
        <li>Break your workflow with slow, bloated interfaces</li>
      </ul>
      <p>ToolMixr is our answer: fast, clean, private. That's it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Who Built This?</h2>
      <p>Hi, I'm Lu Shen. I build web tools for a living — and I got frustrated enough with the existing options that I decided to build my own.</p>
      <p>Before ToolMixr, I was that person with 15 browser tabs open, each running a different "free" tool that required an account, uploaded my data to some server I'd never heard of, or hit me with a paywall after two uses. So I built what I wanted: tools that just work, right in your browser, no strings attached.</p>
      <p>I test every tool myself before publishing it. If a calculator gives me a wrong answer or a generator produces broken output, it doesn't ship. Period.</p>
      <p>When I'm not building tools, I'm probably testing other people's AI tools over on <a href="https://genaipick.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GenAIPick</a>, where I write honest reviews of AI products I actually pay for.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Our Principles</h2>
      <div class="principles-grid">
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">🔒</div>
          <h3>Privacy First</h3>
          <p>All processing happens locally in your browser. Your data never leaves your device.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Instant & Free</h3>
          <p>No sign-up, no limits, no paywalls. Just open and use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">🎯</div>
          <h3>Does One Thing Well</h3>
          <p>Each tool is focused on a single task. No feature creep, no confusion.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>Works Everywhere</h3>
          <p>Desktop, tablet, mobile — all you need is a modern browser.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Available Tools</h2>
      
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>🔍 SEO Tools</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li><a href="/meta-tag-generator">Meta Tag Generator</a> — SEO & Open Graph meta tags</li>
          <li><a href="/og-image-generator">Open Graph Image Generator</a> — Social preview images</li>
          <li><a href="/robots-txt-generator">Robots.txt Generator</a> — Crawl directives for search engines</li>
          <li><a href="/sitemap-generator">Sitemap Generator</a> — XML sitemaps for better indexing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>💻 Developer Tools</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li><a href="/json-formatter">JSON Formatter</a> — Format, validate & beautify JSON</li>
          <li><a href="/base64-encoder-decoder">Base64 Encoder/Decoder</a> — Encode & decode Base64 strings</li>
          <li><a href="/url-encoder-decoder">URL Encoder/Decoder</a> — Encode & decode URLs</li>
          <li><a href="/password-generator">Password Generator</a> — Strong, secure passwords</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>💰 Finance Tools</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li><a href="/mortgage-calculator">Mortgage Calculator</a> — Calculate mortgage payments</li>
          <li><a href="/roi-calculator">ROI Calculator</a> — Calculate return on investment</li>
          <li><a href="/compound-interest-calculator">Compound Interest Calculator</a> — Project investment growth</li>
          <li><a href="/loan-calculator">Loan Calculator</a> — Calculate loan payments and schedules</li>
          <li><a href="/adsense-revenue-calculator">AdSense Revenue Calculator</a> — Estimate ad earnings</li>
          <li><a href="/crypto-profit-calculator">Crypto Profit Calculator</a> — Calculate crypto gains and losses</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>🛠️ Utilities</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li><a href="/word-counter">Word Counter</a> — Words, characters, sentences & paragraphs</li>
          <li><a href="/percentage-calculator">Percentage Calculator</a> — Calculate percentages easily</li>
          <li><a href="/age-calculator">Age Calculator</a> — Calculate exact age in years, months, days</li>
          <li><a href="/bmi-calculator">BMI Calculator</a> — Calculate body mass index</li>
          <li><a href="/tip-calculator">Tip Calculator</a> — Calculate tips and split bills</li>
          <li><a href="/discount-calculator">Discount Calculator</a> — Calculate sale prices and discounts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>🎨 Design Tools</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li><a href="/lorem-ipsum-generator">Lorem Ipsum Generator</a> — Placeholder text for designs</li>
          <li><a href="/color-palette-generator">Color Palette Generator</a> — Beautiful color palettes for web projects</li>
          <li><a href="/qr-code-generator">QR Code Generator</a> — Create QR codes instantly</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Have questions, feedback, or feature requests? We'd love to hear from you. Reach us at <a href="mailto:contact@toolmixr.com">contact@toolmixr.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 40px 0 80px;
  }
  .about-page h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F46E5, #7C3AED);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .about-page .subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .about-section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .about-section ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .about-section ul li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .principle-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .principle-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .principle-card h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .principle-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .tool-category {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .tool-category h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .tool-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .tool-list li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .tool-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .tool-list li a {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }
</style>
